  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patient's anxiety prior to surgery has been linked to more harmful outcome after surgery. The
      investigators aim to evaluate the effect of video information on preoperative anxiety level
      in patients with colorectal cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
